msgstr "Veuillez définir une commande diff ou appuyez sur Annuler."

#: qt/snapshotsdialog.py:102
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"The command \"{cmd}\" cannot be found on this system. Please try something "
"else or press Cancel."
